sequenceDiagram
    autonumber
    participant User as 👤 User
    participant Channel as 💬 Channel<br/>(WhatsApp/Telegram/etc)
    participant Gateway as 🌉 Gateway<br/>WebSocket Server
    participant Router as 🎯 Router &<br/>Session Manager
    participant Agent as 🤖 Pi Agent<br/>Runner
    participant Model as 🧠 AI Model<br/>(OpenAI/Anthropic)
    participant Tools as 🛠️ Tool<br/>Registry
    participant ChannelOut as 📤 Outbound<br/>Channel

    User->>+Channel: 📝 Send message
    Channel->>+Gateway: 📨 Inbound message event
    Gateway->>+Router: 🎯 Route message
    
    Note over Router: 🔍 Resolve session key<br/>(channel + account + peer)
    Router->>+Agent: 📂 Load/create session
    
    Note over Agent: 📚 Load history<br/>⚙️ Apply system prompt
    Agent->>+Model: 🚀 API request<br/>(messages + tools)
    
    rect rgb(240, 248, 255)
        Note over Model,Agent: 🔄 Streaming Response
        loop Stream chunks
            Model-->>Agent: 📊 Stream chunk
            Agent->>Gateway: 📡 Agent event
            Gateway->>ChannelOut: ⌨️ Typing indicator
        end
    end
    
    alt 🛠️ Tool Call Required
        Model-->>Agent: 🔧 Tool call request
        Agent->>+Tools: ⚙️ Execute tool
        Tools-->>-Agent: ✅ Tool result
        Agent->>Model: 🔄 Continue with result
    else 💬 Text Response
        Model-->>-Agent: ✨ Final text
    end
    
    Note over Agent: 💾 Save session state
    Agent-->>-Router: 📋 Response ready
    Router-->>-Gateway: 📮 Final response
    Gateway->>ChannelOut: 📤 Send message
    ChannelOut->>User: 📬 Deliver response